To compile : g++ -o routing routing.cpp
To run : 
	1 - ./routing -top top14.txt -conn NSFNET_100.txt -rt routingtablefile.txt -ft forwardingtablefile.txt -path pathsfile.txt -flag 0 -p 0

	2 - ./routing -top top24.txt -conn ARPANET_100.txt -rt routingtablefile.txt -ft forwardingtablefile.txt -path pathsfile.txt -flag 0 -p 0


Parameters: 
	-flag : 0 -> consider hopdistance
			1 -> consider distance cost metric from input file

	-p    : 0 -> Optimistic Approach
			1 -> Pessimistic Approach